  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 Dead Doves</strong> is a short, singleplayer, fixed-perspective horror story set in the heart of the Appalachian wilderness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/f54180785e4e498f352442021dc4955c.poster.avif?t=1760029972\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/f54180785e4e498f352442021dc4955c.webm?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/f54180785e4e498f352442021dc4955c.mp4?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > It's 2004. The mountains are much older.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as <strong>Marcus Stetson</strong> -- the Most Pathetic Man on Earth -- a seasoned backpacker on the Appalachian Trail who decides to pool his resources to team up one last time with his human firecracker of a trail buddy, <strong>Sean</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/3d0c6b9cde0dd39e74db258d51e5ebdc.poster.avif?t=1760029972\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/3d0c6b9cde0dd39e74db258d51e5ebdc.webm?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/3d0c6b9cde0dd39e74db258d51e5ebdc.mp4?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Their mission is to relive the glory days and embark on one final outing: To pinpoint and find the truth behind the holy grail of urban legends: a mysterious, mythical place known in whispers as the <strong>Ant Farm</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/698a2f1633cfb9027c980722304b4b4c.poster.avif?t=1760029972\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/698a2f1633cfb9027c980722304b4b4c.webm?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/698a2f1633cfb9027c980722304b4b4c.mp4?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During their journey, their bond, will, and wits are put to the test when Mark receives a series of cryptic messages in his dreams from a <strong>haunting, bird-like figure</strong> named <strong>The Wren</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/e4c34431581508666e62e596c2985fd5.poster.avif?t=1760029972\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/e4c34431581508666e62e596c2985fd5.webm?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/e4c34431581508666e62e596c2985fd5.mp4?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you discover why the<strong> birds are dropping dead</strong> -- or will you leave behind <i><strong>nothing but footprints</strong></i>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/774ab338d60f115f90e4e35b0e7ef5d4.poster.avif?t=1760029972\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/774ab338d60f115f90e4e35b0e7ef5d4.webm?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/774ab338d60f115f90e4e35b0e7ef5d4.mp4?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/c7b42a0e43fa3935cf019b5b30b1bb27.avif?t=1760029972\" width=604 height=184 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a fully realized narrative</strong> full of mystery, heart, and mortal terror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Navigate The Wren's peculiar Dove Dreams</strong>, and uncover multiple endings that will affect both your past and future.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoy a cinematic Dovecraftian adventure</strong> -- complete with fully-voiced animated cutscenes & and a rich original score.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience a thrilling psychological horror campaign</strong> with secrets tucked into every corner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve puzzles, crack open mysteries</strong>, and uncover the secrets deep Appalachia holds…</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover beautiful environments, strange locations, and stranger locales</strong> with charmingly disturbing '00s-inspired visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Follow the quest of the hiking duo, Mark and Sean</strong>, on their quest to find the mythical Ant Farm.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/aab5c921450a657fe24258a2e55cbc75.poster.avif?t=1760029972\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/aab5c921450a657fe24258a2e55cbc75.webm?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564540/extras/aab5c921450a657fe24258a2e55cbc75.mp4?t=1760029972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
